International Business Machines fell 2 to 110}, American Express
was down } to 28 and General Electric was down | at 39].
   In over-the-counter trading, Farmers Group was up { at 69}. The
company agreed to a $75-a-share takeover offer from B.A.T.
Industries of Britain.
   The NYSE index was off 1.70 at 146.23. On the American Stock
Exchange, the composite market value index fell 1.54 to 292.52.
